  <!-- Introducción de la actividad -->  
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-actividad-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this Number Talk is to elicit strategies students have for subtracting within 1,000. These understandings help students develop fluency and will be helpful later when students choose between using an algorithm or another strategy to subtract.</p>
  </paragraphs>

